          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Calculated globally, human society consumes the equivalent of 400 years' worth of ancient solar energy (expressed in terms of the net primary productivity of plants during previous geological eras) each year through our use of fossil fuels.&rdquo;</span>
